### ============================================
### PROVENI - COMPANY SUPPLIERS API TESTS
### ============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001

### ============================================
### 1. AUTENTICAÇÃO
### ============================================

### 1.1 Login como MANAGER (usar token abaixo)
# @name managerLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "marina@bonequinhos.com.br",
  "password": "marina123"
}

### 1.2 Login como ADMIN (quando precisar passar companyId manualmente)
# @name adminLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@proveni.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Coloque os tokens abaixo após fazer login
@managerToken = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJjbXBoeHh1ZHMwMDAybHdtbjh1dWdpdHQyIiwiZW1haWwiOiJtYXJpbmFAYm9uZXF1aW5ob3MuY29tLmJyIiwicm9sZSI6Ik1BTkFHRVIiLCJjb21wYW55SWQiOiJjbXBoeHh1M2MwMDAxbHdtbjNkdzhkMXloIiwiaWF0IjoxNzc5NTE5MzU1LCJleHAiOjE3ODAxMjQxNTV9.Q9FQZllQPCIqlMTOnr_TRhVJSSNzIy5PAI9HqMJgxzc
@adminToken   = SEU_TOKEN_ADMIN_AQUI

### ============================================
### 2. POST /company-suppliers/direct
###    Cria um fornecedor e já vincula à empresa
###    Roles permitidas: MANAGER, ADMIN
### ============================================

### 2.1 MANAGER cria fornecedor diretamente
###     (companyId é inferido do token automaticamente)
POST {{baseUrl}}/company-suppliers/direct
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "supplierName": "Fornecedor Direto Ltda",
  "cnpj": "11.111.111/0001-11",
  "email": "contato@fornecedordireto.com",
  "phone": "(11) 91111-1111",
  "responsibleName": "João da Silva"
}

### 2.2 MANAGER cria fornecedor sem responsável (campos opcionais omitidos)
POST {{baseUrl}}/company-suppliers/direct
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "supplierName": "Fornecedor Simples S/A",
  "cnpj": "22.222.222/0001-22",
  "email": "contato@fornecedorsimples.com"
}

### 2.3 ADMIN cria fornecedor passando companyId explicitamente
###     (ADMIN não tem companyId no token, então precisa enviar no body)
POST {{baseUrl}}/company-suppliers/direct
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "supplierName": "Fornecedor via Admin",
  "cnpj": "33.333.333/0001-33",
  "email": "contato@fornecedoradmin.com",
  "phone": "(11) 93333-3333",
  "responsibleName": "Maria Souza",
  "companyId": "ID_DA_EMPRESA_ALVO_AQUI"
}

### 2.4 Testa CNPJ já existente (deve vincular o existente à empresa sem criar novo)
POST {{baseUrl}}/company-suppliers/direct
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "supplierName": "Qualquer Nome",
  "cnpj": "11.111.111/0001-11",
  "email": "qualquer@email.com"
}

### 2.5 Testa body inválido - faltando campos obrigatórios (deve retornar 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/company-suppliers/direct
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "(11) 99999-9999"
}

### ============================================
### 3. GET /company-suppliers
###    Lista os fornecedores ATIVOS da empresa do usuário logado
###    Roles permitidas: MANAGER, ADMIN
### ============================================

### 3.1 MANAGER lista fornecedores da sua empresa
GET {{baseUrl}}/company-suppliers
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### 3.2 ADMIN lista fornecedores (baseado no companyId do token — nulo p/ ADMIN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/company-suppliers
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================
### 4. DELETE /company-suppliers/:supplierId
###    Bloqueia um fornecedor (status → BLOCKED)
###    Roles permitidas: MANAGER, ADMIN
### ============================================

### 4.1 MANAGER bloqueia um fornecedor (substitua pelo supplierId real)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/company-suppliers/ID_DO_SUPPLIER_AQUI
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### 4.2 Tenta bloquear fornecedor inexistente (deve retornar 500 ou 404)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/company-suppliers/id-que-nao-existe
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### ============================================
### 5. TESTES DE AUTORIZAÇÃO
### ============================================

### 5.1 Supplier tenta criar fornecedor (deve retornar 403 Forbidden)
POST {{baseUrl}}/company-suppliers/direct
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_SUPPLIER_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "supplierName": "Tentativa Inválida",
  "cnpj": "99.000.000/0001-00",
  "email": "invalido@teste.com"
}

### 5.2 Sem token (deve retornar 401 Unauthorized)
GET {{baseUrl}}/company-suppliers
